<h2>Pancakes</h2>
<ul>
<li>1 teaspoon of salt.</li>
<li>1.5 cups of milk.</li>
<li>2 cups of flour.</li>
<li>2 eggs.</li>
<li>2 tablespoons sugar.</li>
<li>4 tablespoons of melted butter.</li>
<li>6 teaspoons of baking powder.</li>
</ul>
<p>Makes 10/11 pancakes.</p>
